description: This is an Intense back and forth battle between two of our finest feather weight Wrestlers. Juliette March is our Reigning Champ but Mona Wales has been working her way to the top and today she wants to squash that little shit, Juliette March. Brutal leg scissor holds, Brutal back and forth power exchange. The winner Thoroughly humiliates the loser with trash talk and by pouring Piss on the the loser. Behind the Scenes footage for a bonus of humiliation. See the Real Piss harvested!
title: Season 12 Feather Weight Wrestling Championship
